LYNCH
v.
BROCK, SCOTT & INGERSOLL. No. 321P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 30, 2005. Thomas Brock, for Brock, Scott & Ingersoll.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 14th day of June 2005 by Plaintiff for "Notice of Appeal":

"Motion Dismissed ex mero motu by order of the Court in conference this the 30th day of June 2005."
